1.1
log
@Add a port for foomatic-rip 3.0.2.

foomatic-rip is a filter script (like apsfilter or magicfilter) used by
the printer spoolers to convert the incoming PostScript data into the
printer's native format using a printer/driver specific, but
spooler-independent PPD file.
@
